page.title: 07OUR HOBBIES
page.content: IN MY SPARE TIME I GO TO{GUIDES}.WE WORK ON INTEREST BADGES.ONE OF THE BADGES IS STICHERY.I DID A PICTURE OF BUTTERFLY AND A PERRIOT CUSHION.I AM THE PATROLEADER.SOMETIMES AT GUIDES ON SPECIAL OCCASIONS WE HAVE LOADS OF FOOD AND CAKES.WE SOMETIMES GO TO{CAMP IN THE SUMMER.AT{CAMP}YOU HAVE TO DO A LOT OF HARD WORK.WE HAVE TO CLEAN THE LOOS,PUT OUR TENT UP,WASH UP,COOK, COLLECT WOOD FOR THE FIRE,FETCH WATER, AND MAKE AND AIR OUR BED IN ROLL. I HAVE BEEN GOING{DANCING}FOR 7 YEARS. I STARTED WHEN I WAS 4 YEARS OLD AND I AM 11 YEARS OLD NOW. I DO TAP DANCING, BALLET AND MODERN DANCING I ENJOY MY{DANCING}BECAUSE WE DO EXAMS AND SHOWS.I ALSO ENJOY MY{YOUTH CLUB} BECAUSE WE GO ON TRIPS AND MEET NEW FRIENDS.
